{"tid":789471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉立會外藏氣槍 16歲「學生動源」前成員劉康罪成","createTime":"2018-08-22T09:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T12:35:10.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1d18afda9d8f2d751a9473182f2a7ddfd5ea96","tid":789471,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">涉立會外藏氣槍 16歲「學生動源」前成員劉康罪成</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n去年12月12日於立法會進行《議事規則》期間，學生動源前成員、16歲的劉康於添美道及夏慤道交界管有疑似氣槍的仿製槍械，今於東區裁判法院被裁定一項<span style=\"color: red;\">管有仿製火器罪名</span>成立。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉康早前自辯時指，當日到達集會場地是拍攝集會情況，又指自2016年起，因不時有隨機傷人事件，並曾在住所附近目睹打鬥事件，加上去年11月在其就讀的中學外，目擊有示威者遭反港獨人士襲擊，故擔心自己會因其政治立場而受襲，所以帶氣槍作自衞用途。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：陳凱盈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1297992/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1297992%2F&d=ziFh%2BWx%2FGNpJv%2FqqJ503g3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=74690a29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1297992%2F&h=5e038fee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1297992/</a><br />\n<br />\n係咪即係要禁晒啲氣槍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1ca9d4fcf00f7f23b0ad11ef3505a5eec6dafc","tid":789471,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"拎氣槍緊係捉啦 人地青關會同班5毛都係拎刀刀叉叉最多係斬死人 你依家有機會射痛人 唔撚捉你捉邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3aa581a1071a202d7f957485f892ce401faf6d0","tid":789471,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ad473765eeb09eb43b6f00573441664ab9db0b","tid":789471,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm